   FOOD-SKUBE-BEERCOLUMN _ A weekly beer column by the Michael
Skube of the Atlanta Journal-Constitution. This week: Corona:
Triumph of marketing over merit. (Skube, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   FOOD-CYBERSPICE _ A weekly column looking at the plethora of
recipes on the Internet. (Parham, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   COXNET FOOD PAGE
</P>
<P>
   COXNET FOOD 0622 -- Game for something different? Why not try
some of the trendy meats that offer less fat, more flavor than
beef. (Langhenry, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes
3-column color photo of rack of venison, 18-pica color color photo
of a bison burger, 1-column color photo of Ostrich Panang and
