<HEADLINE>
STUDY FINDS CONTINUED DECLINE IN NUMBER OF SEA OTTERS 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Note optional trim)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JANE KAY  
 c.1999 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
