for more speed in the lineup against the fleet Nigerians, US
women's soccer coach Tony DiCicco may end up fielding the same 11
who blanked Denmark. By John powers.
</P>
<P>
   GLF-LPGA-PAK (Wilmington, Del.) _ Se Ri Pak exploded on the
women's golf scene a year ago at the McDonald's LPGA Championship.
And she's back to try and do it again. By Joe Concannon. 560 words.
</P>
<P>
   WOM-NOTEBOOK (Undated) _ If you've been dismayed by T-shirts
with slogans proclaiming ``Your game's as ugly as your girl'' and
``You can't hold me, that's your girl's job,'' apparently you're
not alone. By Barbara Huebner.
</P>
