</P>
<P>
   101. Lake Forest, IL.............(18,700).......($ 545,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   102. Manhattan Beach, CA.........(31,149).......($ 545,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   103. Woodway, WA.................(993)..........($ 545,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   104. Spring Lake, NJ.............(3,593)........($ 544,500) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   105. Newport Beach, CA...........(69,092).......($ 540,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   106. Burlingame, CA..............(26,666).......($ 537,500) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   107. Rancho Palos Verdes, CA.....(14,293).......($ 535,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   108. Cos Cob, CT.................(7,012)........($ 532,500) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   109. Huntington Bay, NY..........(1,521)........($ 532,500) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   110. Clyde Hill, WA..............(2,865)........($ 530,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   111. Del Mar, CA.................(5,211)........($ 527,000) &QL;
