   THOMPSON-COLUMN (Washington) _ Since both Republican George W.
Bush and Democrat Al Gore are expressing centrist positions, the
manner in which they present themselves is as important as the
messages they convey. In their first official sorties, Bush has
emerged the winner. By ROBERT E. THOMPSON. (Already filed.)
