Europe with a fairly expansive political and policy agenda. Plans
to intensify battery of Republicans for failure of gun legislation,
announce a new environmental initiative, unveil his Medicare plan
and tour poverty-mired regions from Appalachia to an Indian
reservation to talk about new investment to help the poor. Heavy
fund-raising schedule for congressional Democrats and continuing
efforts to juggle the competing Clinton, Hillary, Gore agendas. By
John Broder.
