<P>
   TEXAS-OIL. Project for Houston (Working.) Robin Brown
</P>
<P>
   WISCONSIN-BALDWIN-HEALTH. Rep. Tammy Baldwin, D-Madison, joined
a slew of other Democrats Wednesday in trying to force the
Democrat's Patients Bill of Rights onto the House floor. Baldwin
said the legislation is the first step in her campaign hopes for
revamping the health care system in America. By Elizabeth Hurt (500
words.) By Elizabeth Hurt
</P>
<P>
   -30-
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
