<P>
   COKE-MAIN _ BRUSSELS, Belgium _ The Belgian government today
said it will lift its partial ban on Coca-Cola products once the
company has met certain conditions, including enhancing safety
measures at bottling plants. Coca-Cola Co. has accepted the
conditions, which also include a thorough cleaning of the plants
and better monitoring. Company spokesman Paul Pendergrass said the
