<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    INDUSTRY TO HELP PARENTS USE NEW 'V-CHIP' TO SCREEN TV SHOWS
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (e) entertainment categories.
 &HT;    By RAVEN HILL
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
