</P>
<P>
   SHALIKASHVILI-ESSAY (Seattle) _ The mystery over the fake
Shalikashvili essay has been solved _ sort of. A 2,000-word essay
harshly critical of the Clinton administration's handling of the
Kosovo crisis was erroneously attributed to former Joint Chiefs of
Staff Chairman Gen. John Shalikashvili. George Friedman, a defense
analyst and author from Austin, Texas, has stepped forward to claim
ownership of the article.
</P>
<P>
   By Ed Offley. (Story will move in the ``a'' category.)
</P>
