<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-23 21:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7321 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-WCUP-SOBRERO-NYT &LR;      06-23 0754
