<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-23 21:34 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7347 &Cx1f; tad-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RUN-SPRINTERS24-COX     06-23 0618
