(DEN), in one of DEN's sets. DEN's plan is to create Internet-only
programming, low-budget, niche shows aimed at specific audiences
and release them via streaming video. Newman, former president of
Walt Disney Network Television and Touchstone Television, said his
new endeavor was truly a breed apart. (Kim Kulish/New York Times
Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT5) NEW YORK -- June 23, 1999 -- CIR-HITECH-POCKETS, 6-23 --
The sprawling collection of gadgets that are becoming part of our
everyday life, such as cell phones, pagers, and electronic
