KOSOVO-VILLAGE-2, 6-23 -- A French soldier escorts a group of
ethnic Albanian women to the north side of town on Wednesday.
French peacekeepers have been trying to keep a lid on tensions
between Serbs and ethnic Albanians for several days. Serbs menaced
some people wanting to cross a bridge to the side of town which has
the main hospital, many ethnic Albanian homes and almost the only
