   GOLF _ &UR;  &LR; With an innovative video setup, SwingLab purports to put
golfers ``inside the swing'' of top professionals like Tiger Woods.
The East Bay company is testing its kiosk at Mission Bay driving
range, and is preparing for a national launch at the end of this
month. It's one of numerous high-tech devices aiming to lower
